was like, "boom, boom,"

10
00:00:22,750 --> 00:00:25,083
we had a huge crowd
that was like, "whoo, whoo!"

11
00:00:25,166 --> 00:00:26,958
Then some bad stuff happened
and we were like, "uh-oh!"

12
00:00:27,041 --> 00:00:29,500
But then we all worked
together like, "let's do this!"

13
00:00:29,583 --> 00:00:32,375
Now the legend of Franchouchou
can be like, "go, go!"

14
00:00:32,458 --> 00:00:34,333
Or, at least, I hope so.

15
00:00:35,541 --> 00:00:37,333
[SAKURA]
Saki, look! Here we are!

16
00:00:37,416 --> 00:00:40,000
Saga Rock was so great!

17
00:00:40,083 --> 00:00:41,833
I'm glad we all got to go!

18
00:00:41,916 --> 00:00:43,333
-[SAKI giggles]
-[JUNKO gasps]

19
00:00:43,416 --> 00:00:45,541
[JUNKO] That's the reporter
who wrote about our trip

20
00:00:45,625 --> 00:00:46,750
to the hot spring.

21
00:00:46,833 --> 00:00:48,750
-[AI] We're getting buzz.
-[ALL] Huh?

22
00:00:48,833 --> 00:00:51,500
There've been lots of posts
in the past month.

23
00:00:51,583 --> 00:00:54,000
I think we're about
to see a ton of responses.

24
00:00:54,083 --> 00:00:56,041
Positive and negative.

25
00:00:57,041 --> 00:00:58,125
So cool!

26
00:00:58,208 --> 00:00:59,958
I think I dazzled
people the most!

27
00:01:00,416 --> 00:01:02,250
Really? I don't see you.

28
00:01:02,333 --> 00:01:03,333
Oh, right there!

29
00:01:03,416 --> 00:01:04,458
-[LILY growls]
-[SAKURA giggles]

30
